        <updateDate>2021-07-12T18:08:22Z</updateDate>
        <text>
          <![CDATA[ <p>This resolution expresses the sense of the Senate that access to reliable and clean drinking water is critically important to the health and welfare of American Indians and Alaska Natives. Further, the resolution calls upon the federal government to provide water access to tribal members and communities.</p> </p>]]>
        </text>
